<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5019862>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURES 112–115. Genitalia of Atheta pennsylvanica Bernhauer (male, 8 km S New Windsor, New York (114–115); female, holotype of At. fontis Casey (112); and female, 8 km SEE Springfield, Vermont (113)). 112–113 — spermatheca; 114 — median lobe, parameral view; 115 — median lobe, lateral view. Scale bar 0.1 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/5019862/files/figure.png" .

